#Tarot #Meditation // 8 of Cups + 6 of Cups + Snake 
What is lost in one form is gained in another. We must be willing to perceive that the universe has its own mysterious ways of filling our own cups. Sometimes our wishes are not granted until we demonstrate an act of faith, be that a leap & total plunge into the nothingness or the willingness to leave everything behind in pursuit of your heart's desire. This is an act of a courageous spiritual warrior & is demonstrated by the 8 of Cups. We must be grateful at all times for that which is placed our way. Unbeknownst to us, this is training & preparation for what's to come & you never know what upgrades the cosmos have in store for you. The 8 of Cups is about taking a risk to lead yourself blindly so that you may find the adequate nourishment you need - it is not about a selfish pursuit but the realization of one's greatness & the responsibility in unfolding that. We must learn how to actualize ourselves through the resources given to us & when you have milked all that you can, dare to find another supply somewhere else. Certainly this card denotes a sense of maturity, knowing when to move on & enhance your experience but it also requires that you administer extreme faith, in self & in source because the path is undetermined as you still write it. The 6 of Cups speaks of the familiar or perhaps past life talents visiting you now & being integrated w/ the identity that you now choose to assume. There are many kindred spirits that love & desire to help you along the way. Seek the blessings in the smallest of things; a gift is on its way to you. It is when we seem to steer off course, that in retrospect we realize it was actually the best path we could have ventured on. The 6 of Cups will invite the past into your life, revisit old environments, memories, friends, family, experiences, etc, for comfort & lessons of growth. Perhaps by going backwards you will have successfully completed a karmic cycle left undone. At this time it's important to be in tune w/ your own needs & requirements. There will be others that can subtly persuade you to focus otherwise. Snake reveals your psychic power; trust it at all times.

#buenosdiasvenezuela y el mundo entero!

Quizás una de las cosas que más he aprendido a lo largo de mi camino espiritual, es que el mundo que nos rodea es nuestro espejo, que viene a mostrarnos nuestra propia protección. 
Todo ese caos que vemos afuera, esas guerras, ese hambre, das enfermedades, son sencillamente el reflejo de lo caóticos estamos por dentro, y si queremos que eso de afuera se sabe, tenemos que empezar a sanarnos nosotros. 
Cada vez que atacamos a alguien, cada vez que insultamos a alguien, sencillamente estamos atacándonos nosotros mismos, por tal razón debemos empezar a practicar el amor y la paz dentro de nosotros, si queremos verlo proyectado en el afuera, porque nada cambia si nosotros no cambiamos.
Es por ello que HOY quiero invitarlos a tomar consciencia de nuestras vidas y entender, que todos esos cambios que queremos para el país y el mundo, empiezan dentro de nosotros, solo transformándonos nosotros es que lograremos el éxito y la paz que queremos experimentar.  #yo #psychic #psychicmedium #medium #mediumship #bhagavanvasquez #coach #coaching #motivacion #motivation #inspiracion #inspiration #happiness #felicidad #sabiduria #wisdom #buenosdias #goodmorning #venezuela #vzla #caracas #maracay #valencia #barquisimeto #maracaibo #puertoordaz #mundo #world 🙏🏻😊 Menciona a tus familiares y amigos 😊🙏🏻
